    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a split-sump oiling system designed to withstand high-lateral-G loads. This power unit delivers a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its precision with aluminum multi-link rear suspension and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. Recent service includes a comprehensive analysis of the rod bearings and replacement of the throttle actuators to ensure mechanical longevity. The vehicle exhibits minor aesthetic wear commensurate with its age, but the powertrain and subframe integrity remain excellent, offering a pure, unadulterated M-division driving experience.",
