    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that looks as good as it performs. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though there are minor, typical signs of road use such as a few light stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch. The interior is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a complete service history. We recently performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, which included a fresh oil change, brake fluid flush, and a new cabin air filter. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads are thick. It drives straight and true, with smooth gear transitions and no unusual noises from the suspension. This has been a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle, and it is ready for its next chapter.",
